OL,3,CAlmost 800 shoplifting offences a day
OL,4,Cgo unsolved, study shows
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police had the worst
OL,7,Frecord, with 76.9% of its 93,705
OL,8,Fshoplifting cases closed with no
OL,9,Fsuspect identified and just 5.9%
OL,10,Fresulting in a charge.
OL,12,FAlmost 290,000 shoplifting cases went
OL,13,Funsolved in 2024-25, according to
OL,14,FHouse of Commons library analysis.
OL,16,FThe figures showed 55.5% of
OL,17,Finvestigations in England and Wales
OL,18,Ffailed to identify a suspect, while
OL,19,Fjust 18.3% resulted in a charge.
